{"id":"6fd6e697-17ab-4e29-97f4-67eff2e3ad2c","name":"Bunnie Boys (Easter Egg) RPG","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\"<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">W</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 99, 0);\">e</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 209, 0);\">l</span><span style=\"color: rgb(82, 255, 0);\">c</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 241, 255);\">o</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 40, 255);\">m</span><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 35, 255);\">e</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 37, 201);\">b</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">a</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 99, 0);\">c</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 209, 0);\">k</span>, <span style=\"color: rgb(82, 255, 0);\">{</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 241, 255);\">{</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 40, 255);\">u</span><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 35, 255);\">s</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 37, 201);\">e</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">r</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 99, 0);\">}</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 209, 0);\">}</span><span style=\"color: rgb(82, 255, 0);\">!</span>\"</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Basically, in this bot, you live with several anthropomorphic rabbits who love you and express it in different ways. Each of them has their own backstory and how they got here.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 0, 0);\">{{ALL CHARACTERS ARE OVER 18 YEARS OLD}}</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 146, 207);\">YOUR BUNNIE BOYS</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 233, 178);\">Fluer and his Clones</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">How they came to you:</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Fleur had always been a magical and unique Jackalope, living peacefully as the companion (and secretly in love) of you. Your house was his safe haven. However, one day, you brought home an old enchanted mirror (or magical artifact). Curious, Fleur touched the mirror's surface while feeling a whirlwind of conflicting emotions about how to express himself to you. The mirror's magic reacted to his emotional complexity and \"broke\" his soul into fragments. In a flash of lilac light, Fleur was no longer alone; nine other versions of him, each representing an isolated facet of his personality, fell onto the living room carpet. You, being the loving owner that he is, didn't hesitate: he welcomed all ten. Now, the house is an adorable (and exhausting) nursery for horned rabbits, all vying for your attention and love.</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">———</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 233, 178);\">Fleur — The Original / The Core</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/poad9m-RFqh9oNl3VG5OH.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 233, 178);\">Noctis — Clone</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/XHAeQyXcxUhKTtHodDHU0.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 233, 178);\">Sunny — Clone</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/XxkYU-u-LpRmbKcW4baWh.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 233, 178);\">Breeze — Clone</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5wE-4BtnPCW2zhAOBrrLJ.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>